{
  "chapter": 16,
  "chapter_summary": "第十六回\"死不救\"主要讲述芮玮与熊解花的对峙及后续遭遇。熊解花坦白她因被芮问夫抛弃而投靠高昌国，企图谋杀大将军高寿以报复。神秘黑衣女子救下高莫野，芮玮脱身后前往小五台山寻找名医史不旧。途中遇到一位走火入魔的残臂老人，老人临终前传授芮玮\"大愚剑\"剑法，并透露史不旧住在东南三十里小峰上。老人死去后，芮玮赶赴史不旧竹屋求医，但史不旧以\"来客不见\"为由拒绝。芮玮苦求之下，史不旧开门见高莫野却说\"这人我不救\"，留下悬念。本章展现了芮玮的侠义心肠和对高莫野的深情，同时引入了史不旧这一重要角色。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_jie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "熊解花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我到底曾深深爱他，迄至如今仍未忘怀，是故我不忍心对他直接报复，而间接报复……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "间接报复？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_jie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "熊解花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道他一生对现今兵马大将军忠心耿耿，亦就是对国尽忠，于是我就反其道而行，投身外籍高昌国，专事设法谋杀大将军高寿！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_jie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "熊解花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要高寿一死，当朝邦基必危，西域各国联合起来，兵强马壮中原失去了大兵法家，于是西域各国进攻中原必定势如破竹！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_jie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "熊解花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那时人生国亡，人生对就没有任何乐趣，当我见他痛苦时，我就心满意足了，我多年被弃的仇恨也就报复了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这样报复未免太丧失人性，要知你是汉族人民，投身异族来灭自己的国家，简直猪狗不如！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_jie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "熊解花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好小子你敢骂我！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难怪我父亲不理你，你这种女人，任谁也不会爱你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_jie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "熊解花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我今天拼了不将这丫头送往高昌国，活活摔死在你面前，教你亲眼见她惨死，终生难忘！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你放下她，有种把我摔死，莫要杀害无辜！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_jie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "熊解花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是谁？竟敢抢救姑娘要杀的人！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "多谢前辈！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_jie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "熊解花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "站住，别想逃走！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shu_yong",
      "speaker_name": "王书永",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "何必这么快就走了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阁下可是彩衣教主？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shu_yong",
      "speaker_name": "王书永",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是，阁下可是毒毙本教十余位高手的芮玮吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下并没有毒毙贵教高手，更与彩衣教无冤无仇，敬请教主让开一条方便之路。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shu_yong",
      "speaker_name": "王书永",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要我让开不难，但若不替教中十余人复仇，我王书永还能在江湖上充字号？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下决未毒杀贵教高手，教主为何不信？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shu_yong",
      "speaker_name": "王书永",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阁下若未毒杀本教郑必胜十余人，怎会逃出来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下离开贵教时，他们已经被毒死，但是绝非我所为，此点请教主相信。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shu_yong",
      "speaker_name": "王书永",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我姑且相信你一次，那请问是谁将他们毒死的？总不会是他们自己把自己毒死吧！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个我不便说出，请原谅让路。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shu_yong",
      "speaker_name": "王书永",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好小子，本教主对你客气，你倒狡赖起来，什么不便说，分明是你毒杀的，有证人指出！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "证人是谁？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shu_yong",
      "speaker_name": "王书永",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是花老幺，还要赖不？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下若说花老幺是凶手，证人是我，教主相信否？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shu_yong",
      "speaker_name": "王书永",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花老幺吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_jie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "熊解花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别再跟那小子啰嗦，快快擒下，将那女子送往高昌国便是奇功一件，莫要迟了，这边有姑娘挡住！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shu_yong",
      "speaker_name": "王书永",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "管你们谁是凶手，快快就擒，与花老幺互相对质去，若真非你所为，自会将你释放！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shu_yong",
      "speaker_name": "王书永",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你莫要近身，否则我立即将他俩毙死在掌下……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你……是谁？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我叫芮玮，来此想找一位姓史的名医，不知他住在何处，老丈可知道吗？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那丫头要找史不旧医病？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是，老丈知道路途，请指示在下？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别找他，别找他，我病入膏盲，想请他救活，哪知找到他，求了三天都不肯治，如今我就要死去了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怀中女子与他相识，他一定肯治，治好后，我们求他再给老丈治病，想是没问题的！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别想得那么天真，你怀中女子纵然是他妹妹，他也不肯治的，因他被我紧逼时曾道：就是亲生父母也不救治！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不会的！不会的！请快告诉我史不旧住在何处，我要马上找他，否则我怀中的女子就要死去！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他若救你怀中女子，就不会被称死不救了！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老丈若能告知史不旧住处，晚辈愿为老丈做一切事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你且坐下来。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你以前学过武功没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "学过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那你演一套剑法给我看看！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那女子是你的妻子吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你别心急，好好跟我待一段时间，于你有莫大的好处，那时我再告诉你史不旧在何处，否则你盲目找去，十天也找不到。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "剑法尚不差，可惜功力太差，而且又不熟练！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你去吧！别烦我啦！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那史不旧住在何处，请老丈告知？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你先骗我，当然我也要骗你。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我何曾骗过你？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你当我老了，眼睛不行吗？你能使出那套玄妙的剑法，却无丝毫功力，骗得谁来？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来如此，老丈错怪了，我因曾吸入'神仙倒'这种迷香药，至使功力丧失！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你什么时候吸到'神仙倒'？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "八天前。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那不错呀！闻说'神仙倒'被吸进后，十三天内不能行动自如，你仅八天便能如此，想是内功定然不错？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我自幼跟先父学过龟息大功。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "龟息大功！那你是'掌剑飞'芮问夫的儿子了，是吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "晚辈先父正是'掌剑飞'。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这样可好啦！你既学过龟息大功，有资格跟我学一招剑法，这招剑法十分艰难，我望你一天内学会……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么啦？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一天内，你定要将我教你的剑法记住！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老丈，你先告诉我史不旧住在何处，我将她送到那里后，定然回来跟老丈专心学剑！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不行！你跟我学完剑后，我才告诉你！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不告诉我算了，且去碰碰运气，倘若不幸她死了，我就陪她一死，世上没有什么了不得的事……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "且慢！你回来慢慢商谈。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若先告诉你史不旧住处，你去后，万一他不肯救治，或者无法再救，你一定伤心欲绝，那时怎有心情来跟我学剑法，所以我才要你先学剑再去，并非我不顾人情，定要你先学剑……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在没有救愈她之前，我也无心学剑！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "况且……况且……我的性命只有一天了……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老丈，芮玮尽力在一天内跟你学会那招剑法。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要想学会决不可能，我只望你记下就好，你仔细听我说，这招剑法叫大愚剑……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你现在已能完全记住大愚剑，只要勤练一段时日，这招剑法的威力不难被你完全学会，现在我该告诉你史不旧住在何处……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还记得昨天说过，我告诉你史不旧住处后，将要替我做事吗……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要老丈吩咐下来，晚辈定去办成！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我且先告诉你史不旧的住处，他住在此去东南三十里外的一个小峰上，你只要一直走去定可找到！",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但不知老丈要我做一件什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "去……去……摩……霄……峰……明年……八……月…中……秋",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你可知传我一剑，要我帮你去敌对的人，就是我吗……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "瞎子！没看到门旁那块牌子吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看是看到了，但……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看到就好，没有什么但不但，快滚吧！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "晚辈有个病人，马上就要死了！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死了活该，管我屁事！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "前辈是不是人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然是人，而且是个很好的人……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "前辈既自称好人，请救晚辈友人一命！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你再叫也没有用，史某虽是好人，却发誓不救人性命，小伙子不要白费时间，去想别的办法吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 369
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "前辈不救人性命，江湖上号称'死不救'，晚辈早已知道，但晚辈这个友人，前辈只要出来一见，一定肯救。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这小子倒老实，史某还不知江湖上叫我死不救，史不旧！死不救！哈哈，我这个名字取得正好！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请前辈出来一见可好？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "世上还有一人，我是一定要救的，要是那人是你友人，我一定就救……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是，晚辈这友人就是前辈一定要救的人！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 387,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "前辈，此人你一定会救的。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人我不救！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    }
